text: Mary Abigail Wambach (born June 2, 1980) is an American retired soccer player, coach, and member of the National Soccer Hall of Fame. She won the U.S. Soccer Athlete of the Year award six times. She played for the U.S. women's national soccer team from 2003 to 2015. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:American soccer players Category:Sportspeople from Rochester, New York
